{"tid":1915000,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"其實咩叫救命？","createTime":"2020-03-08T02:03:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-08T07:46:27.000Z","uid":69159,"like":10,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c92bf94cae0abbcd61234ce324da23588d4d46c8","tid":1915000,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:03:33.000Z","msg":"救命<br />\n[help]：常用於表示處於危難之中的人的叫喚<br />\n救命！<br />\n<br />\n但救命一詞，係香港間唔中都會聽到，當你聽到後嘅反應會係點呢？？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果改成：「有xx想殺我，有xx想掉我落樓」<br />\n或者提供更加確實嘅資料<br />\n等聽到嘅人可以查返，救到你，會唔會更好？（理想化）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n例如：<br />\n特工想殺死我，陳大明1803室<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可"},{"pid":"6d3b82af21478f10ab7c517d7f9b3e100850c4fa","tid":1915000,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:07:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"541fea5fe8c5596239bb967fe258061f5b16db6c","tid":1915000,"uid":167506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"有次聽到有人係公園嗌救命 去到點知係pair情侶玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ff24b9b3a47215080e0047fee361fecd95ec6f8","tid":1915000,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:13:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"08a113b41fa43f42de3f9030b3cc8276dd0a9b36","tid":1915000,"uid":176553,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:13:32.000Z","msg":"聽人講過叫火足，最多人會理"},{"pid":"b7eb5501d74ec6056a42a6d9aa60664fd8050ba1","tid":1915000,"uid":52605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"541fea5fe8c5596239bb967fe258061f5b16db6c","tid":1915000,"uid":167506,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:11:42.000Z","msg":"有次聽到有人係公園嗌救命 去到點知係pair情侶玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-08T02:14:12.000Z","msg":"救命真係唔好亂叫"},{"pid":"b1b757b6f6020f5d75db4336641e55b8238bae5c","tid":1915000,"uid":69159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":